						               													<description>Take on the role of mighty shape shifters. By using powerful attacks and assuming the form of mighty beasts the shifters do battle to see who will reign supreme. The first player to empty their hand is the winner of the duel and can lay claim to the title of the Ultimate Shape Shifter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Select a Form - Each player selects one Form Card from their stack of face down Form Cards and places in the center of the table but in front of them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Select a Combat Style - Each player then selects one of their combat style cards from their hand and places it face down besides their form card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Reveal - All cards are flipped face up.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Resolution: The success of a combat style depends on the form.&amp;#10;If successful, players put the Combat Style Card face down in the discard pile.&amp;#10;If unsuccessful, players put the combat style card back in their hand.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;End of turn - Players put the Form Card they just used aside, face-up and return any previously used Form Cards back to their stack.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Winning&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when a player ends a turn with no Combat Style Cards in their hand.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Note&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This contains all three Transmogrification Games; Transmogrification, Advance Transmogrification and Epic Transmogrification.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
